metadata.abstract: The document 'Above FL285 - Bremen FIR' provides detailed information about the air traffic control sectors within the Bremen FIR (EDWW) above flight level 285. It includes login details, sector indicators, frequencies, and callsigns for various sectors such as Ostsee Low (OSE12), Ostsee High (OSE22), Havel Low (HVL12), and Havel High (HVL22). The document is intended for flight simulator use only and is not to be used for real-world flight. It also lists the sector owners for each sector, indicating which controllers are responsible for specific areas. Additionally, it mentions that EDUU_H_CTR will cover EDUU sectors SAL and SPE, which are part of the EDMM FIR on VATSIM, and requires a familiarisation session for EDMM HOF before staffing EDUU_H_CTR.
